title: Latest Buildings (Points) in Haiti, GeoFabrik, February 8, 2010
name: Latest Buildings (Points) in Haiti, GeoFabrik, February 8, 2010
description: This is a csv of the latest buildings data from Open Street Map extracts provided by GeoFabrik. This data shows the buildings as points. I simply downloaded the shapefile of buildings from Public as a csv, saved, and reuploaded. This data was updated on February 8, 2010.
